Run Random test with coverage ON.
=================================
% vcs -ntb -f ./risc8_ova.files -cm line+cond+fsm+tgl +vc ../../directc/alu.c ../../directc/decoder.c -l risc8.comp.log $*
% simv +random -cm line+cond+fsm+tgl -ova_report risc8.ova.log -l risc8.run.log

        You can observe that randomization has helped in improving the coverage
        of the DUT.
% vcs -cm_pp gui -cm line+cond+fsm+tgl
To run the example:
	Use Makefile
